{"tid":2510482,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇清嘅媽媽好驚貓，但最終都養到貓？","createTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T07:49:38.000Z","uid":1823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea7800e0ddeb13048120cd5920b8750e6d7acf9","tid":2510482,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"上星期問老母比唔比養貓，仆街原來老母好撚驚貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該話所有會走來走去嘅動物都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我細個養甲蟲佢反而唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試過提議帶佢去貓Cafe試吓先，佢又唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓全能嘅連登仔有冇妙計教到老母唔驚貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7a6f7067377c85f0f6f62ec0b3e0e1713f0258","tid":2510482,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:50.000Z","msg":"你扮貓"},{"pid":"7b5692b49cb1ea0852d43e7a8336dc9df6383f43","tid":2510482,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好想講叫佢食返一兩隻先.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先斬後奏"},{"pid":"6d8b6c64d7fa5628e4030ecbb02f8df12c7e9e8f","tid":2510482,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"驚就唔驚<br />\n不過養之前屌到我仆街又話自己敏感又乜又物<br />\n<br />\n而家日日同2隻貓玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11d8a4d72c2954b5e37579f575754d944f9d3c1","tid":2510482,"uid":117237,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"自己冇經濟能力搬出去<br />\n又要迫鳩屋企人接受自己喜好<br />\n做人做到咁撚廢又自私<br />\n唔好害尻d貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cc727da431956811c0eaf3dd9085083d859da8","tid":2510482,"uid":306217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"如果老母本身有責任心就先斬後奏<br />\n冇乜責任心就唔好喇 一陣逼你棄養<br />\n利申 老母敏感 先斬後奏養貓 最後養到終老喊得最慘係老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5757a4757db5dba39080dce47e9bb36bdee5c0","tid":2510482,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"貓毛敏感?<br />\n定係未接觸過貓,先話驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0602b689ec03409c2085029d5720eabfbe856334","tid":2510482,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"問下老豆，老母有冇扮過貓？<br />\n未扮過就叫佢扮下<br />\n扮過就買得<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3b61b3ca4b3dc46e1f7bcb7765afdd1530a928","tid":2510482,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ea7800e0ddeb13048120cd5920b8750e6d7acf9","tid":2510482,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"上星期問老母比唔比養貓，仆街原來老母好撚驚貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該話所有會走來走去嘅動物都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我細個養甲蟲佢反而唔